Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Kamala Harris was the ORIGINAL Marxist District Attorney—she destroyed San Francisco, and she will destroy our Country. Harris supports ending cash bail nationwide, which means releasing violent criminals immediately after arrest. She wants to abolish jail sentences for parole violators, she endorsed DE-FUNDING THE POLICE, and she sponsored a bill to strip police officers of legal protection, leaving our communities at the mercy of deranged criminals and violent mobs!
